    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[[转发]史上最全web.xml配置文件元素详解]]></title>
      <url>http://www.allenleung.tk/2017/02/14/2017-02-14.%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%91-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%85%A8web-xml%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="web-xml配置文件常用元素及其意义预览"><a href="#web-xml配置文件常用元素及其意义预览" class="headerlink" title="web.xml配置文件常用元素及其意义预览"></a>web.xml配置文件常用元素及其意义预览</h3><a id="more"></a>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"> 1 &lt;web-app&gt;</div><div class="line"> 2 </div><div class="line"> 3      &lt;!--定义了WEB应用的名字--&gt;</div><div class="line"> 4      &lt;display-name&gt;&lt;/display-name&gt;</div><div class="line"> 5 </div><div class="line"> 6      &lt;!--声明WEB应用的描述信息--&gt;</div><div class="line"> 7      &lt;description&gt;&lt;/description&gt;</div><div class="line"> 8 </div><div class="line"> 9      &lt;!--context-param元素声明应用范围内的初始化参数--&gt;</div><div class="line">10      &lt;context-param&gt;&lt;/context-param&gt;</div><div class="line">11 </div><div class="line">12      &lt;!--过滤器元素将一个名字与一个实现javax.servlet.Filter接口的类相关联--&gt;</div><div class="line">13      &lt;filter&gt;&lt;/filter&gt;</div><div class="line">14 </div><div class="line">15      &lt;!--一旦命名了一个过滤器，就要利用filter-mapping元素把它与一个或多个servlet或JSP页面相关联--&gt;</div><div class="line">16      &lt;filter-mapping&gt;&lt;/filter-mapping&gt;</div><div class="line">17 </div><div class="line">18      &lt;!--servlet API的版本2.3增加了对事件监听程序的支持，事件监听程序在建立、修改和删除会话或servlet环境时得到通知。</div><div class="line">19          Listener元素指出事件监听程序类--&gt;</div><div class="line">20      &lt;listener&gt;&lt;/listener&gt;</div><div class="line">21 </div><div class="line">22      &lt;!--在向servlet或JSP页面制定初始化参数或定制URL时，必须首先命名servlet或JSP页面。</div><div class="line">23          Servlet元素就是用来完成此项任务的--&gt;</div><div class="line">24      &lt;servlet&gt;&lt;/servlet&gt;</div><div class="line">25 </div><div class="line">26      &lt;!--服务器一般为servlet提供一个缺省的URL：http://host/webAppPrefix/servlet/ServletName。</div><div class="line">27          但是，常常会更改这个URL，以便servlet可以访问初始化参数或更容易地处理相对URL。</div><div class="line">28          在更改缺省URL时，使用servlet-mapping元素--&gt;</div><div class="line">29      &lt;servlet-mapping&gt;&lt;/servlet-mapping&gt;</div><div class="line">30 </div><div class="line">31      &lt;!--如果某个会话在一定时间内未被访问，服务器可以抛弃它以节省内存。可通过使用HttpSession的</div><div class="line">32          setMaxInactiveInterval方法明确设置单个会话对象的超时值，或者可利用session-config元素制定缺省超时值--&gt;</div><div class="line">33      &lt;session-config&gt;&lt;/session-config&gt;</div><div class="line">34 </div><div class="line">35      &lt;!--如果Web应用具有想到特殊的文件，希望能保证给他们分配特定的MIME类型，则mime-mapping元素提供这种保证--&gt;</div><div class="line">36      &lt;mime-mapping&gt;&lt;/mime-mapping&gt;</div><div class="line">37 </div><div class="line">38      &lt;!--指示服务器在收到引用一个目录名而不是文件名的URL时，使用哪个文件--&gt;</div><div class="line">39      &lt;welcome-file-list&gt;&lt;/welcome-file-list&gt;</div><div class="line">40 </div><div class="line">41      &lt;!--在返回特定HTTP状态代码时，或者特定类型的异常被抛出时，能够制定将要显示的页面--&gt;</div><div class="line">42      &lt;error-page&gt;&lt;/error-page&gt;</div><div class="line">43 </div><div class="line">44      &lt;!--对标记库描述符文件（Tag Libraryu Descriptor file）指定别名。此功能使你能够更改TLD文件的位置，</div><div class="line">45          而不用编辑使用这些文件的JSP页面--&gt;</div><div class="line">46      &lt;taglib&gt;&lt;/taglib&gt;</div><div class="line">47 </div><div class="line">48      &lt;!--声明与资源相关的一个管理对象--&gt;</div><div class="line">49      &lt;resource-env-ref&gt;&lt;/resource-env-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">50 </div><div class="line">51      &lt;!--声明一个资源工厂使用的外部资源--&gt;</div><div class="line">52      &lt;resource-ref&gt;&lt;/resource-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">53 </div><div class="line">54      &lt;!--制定应该保护的URL。它与login-config元素联合使用--&gt;</div><div class="line">55      &lt;security-constraint&gt;&lt;/security-constraint&gt;</div><div class="line">56 </div><div class="line">57      &lt;!--指定服务器应该怎样给试图访问受保护页面的用户授权。它与sercurity-constraint元素联合使用--&gt;</div><div class="line">58      &lt;login-config&gt;&lt;/login-config&gt;</div><div class="line">59 </div><div class="line">60      &lt;!--给出安全角色的一个列表，这些角色将出现在servlet元素内的security-role-ref元素的role-name子元素中。</div><div class="line">61          分别地声明角色可使高级IDE处理安全信息更为容易--&gt;</div><div class="line">62      &lt;security-role&gt;&lt;/security-role&gt;</div><div class="line">63 </div><div class="line">64      &lt;!--声明Web应用的环境项--&gt;</div><div class="line">65      &lt;env-entry&gt;&lt;/env-entry&gt;</div><div class="line">66 </div><div class="line">67      &lt;!--声明一个EJB的主目录的引用--&gt;</div><div class="line">68      &lt;ejb-ref&gt;&lt;/ejb-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">69 </div><div class="line">70      &lt;!--声明一个EJB的本地主目录的应用--&gt;</div><div class="line">71      &lt;ejb-local-ref&gt;&lt;/ejb-local-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">72 </div><div class="line">73  &lt;/web-app&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="各个配置元素详解"><a href="#各个配置元素详解" class="headerlink" title="各个配置元素详解"></a>各个配置元素详解</h3><p>1.Web应用图标：指出IDE和GUI工具用来表示Web应用的大图标和小图标<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;icon&gt;  </div><div class="line">2      &lt;small-icon&gt;/images/app_small.gif&lt;/small-icon&gt;  </div><div class="line">3      &lt;large-icon&gt;/images/app_large.gif&lt;/large-icon&gt;  </div><div class="line">4  &lt;/icon&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>2.Web 应用名称：提供GUI工具可能会用来标记这个特定的Web应用的一个名称<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;display-name&gt;Tomcat Example&lt;/display-name&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>3.Web 应用描述：给出于此相关的说明性文本<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;disciption&gt;Tomcat Example servlets and JSP pages.&lt;/disciption&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>4.上下文参数：声明应用范围内的初始化参数<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;context-param&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;param-name&gt;参数名&lt;/para-name&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;param-value&gt;参数值&lt;/param-value&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;description&gt;参数描述&lt;/description&gt;</div><div class="line">5  &lt;/context-param&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>在servlet里面可以通过 getServletContext().getInitParameter(“context/param”)得到</p>
<p>5.过滤器配置：将一个名字与一个实现javaxs.servlet.Filter接口的类相关联<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"> 1 &lt;filter&gt;</div><div class="line"> 2      &lt;filter-name&gt;setCharacterEncoding&lt;/filter-name&gt;</div><div class="line"> 3      &lt;filter-class&gt;com.myTest.setCharacterEncodingFilter&lt;/filter-class&gt;</div><div class="line"> 4      &lt;init-param&gt;</div><div class="line"> 5          &lt;param-name&gt;encoding&lt;/param-name&gt;</div><div class="line"> 6          &lt;param-value&gt;GB2312&lt;/param-value&gt;</div><div class="line"> 7      &lt;/init-param&gt;</div><div class="line"> 8  &lt;/filter&gt;</div><div class="line"> 9  &lt;filter-mapping&gt;</div><div class="line">10      &lt;filter-name&gt;setCharacterEncoding&lt;/filter-name&gt;</div><div class="line">11      &lt;url-pattern&gt;/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt;</div><div class="line">12  &lt;/filter-mapping&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>6.监听器配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;listener&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;listerner-class&gt;org.springframework.web.context.ContextLoaderListener&lt;/listener-class&gt;</div><div class="line">3  &lt;/listener&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>7.Servlet配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"> 1 &lt;servlet&gt;</div><div class="line"> 2    &lt;servlet-name&gt;servlet名称&lt;/servlet-name&gt;</div><div class="line"> 3    &lt;servlet-class&gt;servlet类全路径&lt;/servlet-class&gt;</div><div class="line"> 4    &lt;init-param&gt;</div><div class="line"> 5        &lt;param-name&gt;参数名&lt;/param-name&gt;</div><div class="line"> 6        &lt;param-value&gt;参数值&lt;/param-value&gt;</div><div class="line"> 7    &lt;/init-param&gt;</div><div class="line"> 8    &lt;run-as&gt;</div><div class="line"> 9        &lt;description&gt;Security role for anonymous access&lt;/description&gt;</div><div class="line">10        &lt;role-name&gt;tomcat&lt;/role-name&gt;</div><div class="line">11    &lt;/run-as&gt;</div><div class="line">12 　 &lt;load-on-startup&gt;指定当Web应用启动时，装载Servlet的次序&lt;/load-on-startup&gt;</div><div class="line">13 &lt;/servlet&gt;</div><div class="line">14 &lt;servlet-mapping&gt;</div><div class="line">15   &lt;servlet-name&gt;servlet名称&lt;/servlet-name&gt;</div><div class="line">16   &lt;url-pattern&gt;映射路径&lt;/url-pattern&gt;</div><div class="line">17 &lt;/servlet-mapping&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>8.会话超时配置（单位为分钟）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;session-config&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;session-timeout&gt;120&lt;/session-timeout&gt;</div><div class="line">3  &lt;/session-config&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>9.MIME类型配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;mime-mapping&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;extension&gt;htm&lt;/extension&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;mime-type&gt;text/html&lt;/mime-type&gt;</div><div class="line">4  &lt;/mime-mapping&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>10.指定欢迎文件页配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1  &lt;welcome-file-list&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;welcome-file&gt;index.jsp&lt;/welcome-file&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;welcome-file&gt;index.html&lt;/welcome-file&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;welcome-file&gt;index.htm&lt;/welcome-file&gt;</div><div class="line">5  &lt;/welcome-file-list&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>11.配置错误页面</p>
<p>　　(1).通过错误码来配置error-page<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;!--配置了当系统发生404错误时，跳转到错误处理页面NotFound.jsp--&gt;</div><div class="line">2 &lt;error-page&gt;</div><div class="line">3       &lt;error-code&gt;404&lt;/error-code&gt;</div><div class="line">4       &lt;location&gt;/NotFound.jsp&lt;/location&gt;</div><div class="line">5  &lt;/error-page&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>　　(2).通过异常的类型配置error-page<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;!--配置了当系统发生java.lang.NullException（即空指针异常）时，跳转到错误处理页面error.jsp--&gt;</div><div class="line">2 &lt;error-page&gt;</div><div class="line">3       &lt;exception-type&gt;java.lang.NullException&lt;/exception-type&gt;</div><div class="line">4       &lt;location&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/location&gt;</div><div class="line">5 &lt;/error-page&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>12.TLD配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;taglib&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;taglib-uri&gt;http://jakarta.apache.org/tomcat/debug-taglib&lt;/taglib-uri&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;taglib-location&gt;/WEB-INF/jsp/debug-taglib.tld&lt;/taglib-location&gt;</div><div class="line">4  &lt;/taglib&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>如果开发工具一直在报错,应该把<taglib> 放到 <jsp-config>中<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;jsp-config&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;taglib&gt;</div><div class="line">3          &lt;taglib-uri&gt;http://jakarta.apache.org/tomcat/debug-taglib&lt;/taglib-uri&gt;</div><div class="line">4          &lt;taglib-location&gt;/WEB-INF/pager-taglib.tld&lt;/taglib-location&gt;</div><div class="line">5      &lt;/taglib&gt;</div><div class="line">6  &lt;/jsp-config&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>13.资源管理对象配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;resource-env-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;resource-env-ref-name&gt;jms/StockQueue&lt;/resource-env-ref-name&gt;</div><div class="line">3  &lt;/resource-env-ref&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>14.资源工厂配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;resource-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;res-ref-name&gt;mail/Session&lt;/res-ref-name&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;res-type&gt;javax.mail.Session&lt;/res-type&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;res-auth&gt;Container&lt;/res-auth&gt;</div><div class="line">5 &lt;/resource-ref&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>　　配置数据库连接池就可在此配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1  &lt;resource-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;description&gt;JNDI JDBC DataSource of shop&lt;/description&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;res-ref-name&gt;jdbc/sample_db&lt;/res-ref-name&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;res-type&gt;javax.sql.DataSource&lt;/res-type&gt;</div><div class="line">5      &lt;res-auth&gt;Container&lt;/res-auth&gt;</div><div class="line">6  &lt;/resource-ref&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>15.安全限制配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"> 1 &lt;security-constraint&gt;</div><div class="line"> 2      &lt;display-name&gt;Example Security Constraint&lt;/display-name&gt;</div><div class="line"> 3      &lt;web-resource-collection&gt;</div><div class="line"> 4          &lt;web-resource-name&gt;Protected Area&lt;/web-resource-name&gt;</div><div class="line"> 5          &lt;url-pattern&gt;/jsp/security/protected/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt;</div><div class="line"> 6          &lt;http-method&gt;DELETE&lt;/http-method&gt;</div><div class="line"> 7          &lt;http-method&gt;GET&lt;/http-method&gt;</div><div class="line"> 8          &lt;http-method&gt;POST&lt;/http-method&gt;</div><div class="line"> 9          &lt;http-method&gt;PUT&lt;/http-method&gt;</div><div class="line">10      &lt;/web-resource-collection&gt;</div><div class="line">11      &lt;auth-constraint&gt;</div><div class="line">12          &lt;role-name&gt;tomcat&lt;/role-name&gt;</div><div class="line">13          &lt;role-name&gt;role1&lt;/role-name&gt;</div><div class="line">14      &lt;/auth-constraint&gt;</div><div class="line">15 &lt;/security-constraint&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>16.登陆验证配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1  &lt;login-config&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;auth-method&gt;FORM&lt;/auth-method&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;realm-name&gt;Example-Based Authentiation Area&lt;/realm-name&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;form-login-config&gt;</div><div class="line">5          &lt;form-login-page&gt;/jsp/security/protected/login.jsp&lt;/form-login-page&gt;</div><div class="line">6          &lt;form-error-page&gt;/jsp/security/protected/error.jsp&lt;/form-error-page&gt;</div><div class="line">7      &lt;/form-login-config&gt;</div><div class="line">8  &lt;/login-config&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>17.安全角色：security-role元素给出安全角色的一个列表，这些角色将出现在servlet元素内的security-role-ref元素的role-name子元素中。<br>分别地声明角色可使高级IDE处理安全信息更为容易。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;security-role&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;role-name&gt;tomcat&lt;/role-name&gt;</div><div class="line">3  &lt;/security-role&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>18.Web环境参数：env-entry元素声明Web应用的环境项<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;env-entry&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;env-entry-name&gt;minExemptions&lt;/env-entry-name&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;env-entry-value&gt;1&lt;/env-entry-value&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;env-entry-type&gt;java.lang.Integer&lt;/env-entry-type&gt;</div><div class="line">5 &lt;/env-entry&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>19.EJB 声明<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1 &lt;ejb-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;description&gt;Example EJB reference&lt;/decription&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;ejb-ref-name&gt;ejb/Account&lt;/ejb-ref-name&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;ejb-ref-type&gt;Entity&lt;/ejb-ref-type&gt;</div><div class="line">5      &lt;home&gt;com.mycompany.mypackage.AccountHome&lt;/home&gt;</div><div class="line">6      &lt;remote&gt;com.mycompany.mypackage.Account&lt;/remote&gt;</div><div class="line">7  &lt;/ejb-ref&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>20.本地EJB声明<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1  &lt;ejb-local-ref&gt;</div><div class="line">2      &lt;description&gt;Example Loacal EJB reference&lt;/decription&gt;</div><div class="line">3      &lt;ejb-ref-name&gt;ejb/ProcessOrder&lt;/ejb-ref-name&gt;</div><div class="line">4      &lt;ejb-ref-type&gt;Session&lt;/ejb-ref-type&gt;</div><div class="line">5      &lt;local-home&gt;com.mycompany.mypackage.ProcessOrderHome&lt;/local-home&gt;</div><div class="line">6      &lt;local&gt;com.mycompany.mypackage.ProcessOrder&lt;/local&gt;</div><div class="line">7  &lt;/ejb-local-ref&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h3><p>　　以上就是常用的web.xml中元素的配置以及作用了，欢迎提出异议和不适当的地方共同学习。</p>
]]></content>
